      <title>谨慎的投资者谨慎对待 Petroperu 的扭亏为盈承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/wary-investors-treat-petroperu-turnaround-promises-with-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚历杭德罗·纳瓦埃斯 (Alejandro Narvaez) 以秘鲁国有石油生产商董事长的身份首次公开露面，引发投资者担忧，他们试图判断新政府是否能够为这家陷入困境的公司带来期待已久的转机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/wary-investors-treat-petroperu-turnaround-promises-with-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 15:13:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
