      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/snb-s-equity-too-small-for-balance-sheet-risks-schlegel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行行长马丁·施莱格尔表示，瑞士央行的股本远远低于其庞大的资产负债表带来的风险。]]></description>
